{"tid":440990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★廉署變勞工處？公屋護衛員虛報值勤表，被廉署起訴?!","createTime":"2017-10-19T09:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T11:35:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e7be22e993a5ace4f8afe4e0c1899aed8c3ebb67","tid":440990,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:08:33.000Z","msg":"一名負責巡邏公屋的護衛員虛報值勤表，被廉署起訴，在沙田裁判法院認罪，判囚兩個月，並須向所屬保安公司賠償虛報值勤涉及的16000多元。<br />\n<br />\n案情透露，63歲被告案發時任職房署外判保安公司護衛員，負責沙田區公共屋邨巡邏。他在警誡下接受廉署人員會面時承認，當被委派到兩個屋邨巡邏時，在屋邨辦事處一次過簽到4次，之後就離開崗位，期間60次離開香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1360173-20171019.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1360173-20171019.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=awM1WCYJ6JNa6LRpoiqvWi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=005fb3b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1360173-20171019.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=66e35e62\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1360173-20171019.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a07fd87f407b5a98aa0ba4924a2f33d0ce18afb3","tid":440990,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:09:31.000Z","msg":"搞乜鳩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第時僱主欠薪，搵icac?"},{"pid":"240a47cd9fdc16bebb8a03d46fae5db11cf0d2ac","tid":440990,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:11:05.000Z","msg":"唔使反貪咪去R嘢做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87da3458e040ef57c35017d98e2e68f7a76cad5c","tid":440990,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔使反貪咪去R嘢做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都冇理由做勞工處，得閒不如去執紙皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8